
/*
 *			Thix File System structure:
 *
 *  -------------------------------------------------------------------------
 *  | BB | SB | SSBL | BBL ... |    C0    |    C1    |    C2    | ....	    |
 *  -------------------------------------------------------------------------
 *
 *  BB   - boot block
 *  SB   - superblock
 *  SSBL - second stage boot loader
 *  BBL  - bad blocks list
 *  C0   - cluster number 0
 *  C1   - cluster number 1
 *  C2   - cluster number 2
 *
 *			Thix File System Cluster structure:
 *
 *  -------------------------------------------------------------------------
 *  | SBB | IBMP | BBMP |       Inodes        |            Blocks	    |
 *  -------------------------------------------------------------------------
 *
 *  SBB  - superblock backup
 *  IBMP - inodes bitmap
 *  BBMP - blocks bitmap
 *
 */
